Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.96,0:00:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:09.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:13.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:15.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-U-Uh, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:20.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus's Raijin Tribe have come and attacked \Nin the middle of the Harvest Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:23.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They ruined the Miss Fairy Tail Contest, \Nand took the contestants hostage,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:25.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and now they've started some battle game!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:27.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:30.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Except I happened to be stoned right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:03.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like there's some \Ntrouble at Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:05.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:08.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their members are fighting \Namongst each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:13.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just quarreling, they've \Nbeen seriously going at each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:16.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope their big parade, \NFantasia, will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:23.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:26.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go crazy in the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:27.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Citizens?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:34.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It seems the rules inside the \Nrune barriers only affect wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:35.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Visitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:36.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nab!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Play nice and let yourself get blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:43.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't put you to sleep, \NI can't go search for Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:46.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be \Nfighting amongst ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:48.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but if that's the way you want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen through your plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:58.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're planning a surprise attack \Nusing your Sand Magic, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:01.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your specialty, Telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if you know it's coming, \Nyou can't dodge my attack, Warren!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I can read your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty flashy for some festival show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:13.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of troublemakers they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:19.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat your Friends to Save your Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:25.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for Mira-chan! Now \Nhurry and take defeat like a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A married man shouldn't be \Nlusting after her like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you should talk, divorcee!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laki! Yeah, it's the Harvest Festival, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:35.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the sudden style change?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks slutty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gunning for the Miss Fairy Tail Contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was cut my hair, \Nand look at all the fuss...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:44.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a {\i1}bad{\i0}-girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:45.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:46.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:51.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Max vs. Warren.  Winner: Warren.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vistar vs. Nab. Winner: Nab.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:04.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laki took out four, Macao vs. \NWakaba's battle is in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:07.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Stop this, you foolish children!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:10.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rune traps have been set \Nup throughout the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:13.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the ones who are trapped \Ninside are forced to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:17.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Battle of Fairy \NTail that Laxus talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna join, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he's upset about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:31.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this invisible wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:36.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you plan to do by joining in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:38.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tournament to see who's the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this a tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:45.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all just Laxus's plan to \Nget us to wipe each other out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:49.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we can defeat the Raijin \NTribe within the time limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza and the other girls will turn to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is doing whatever \Nthey can to prevent that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:58.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll need something more than our usual way \Nof thinking to take control of the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:02.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate everyone who was turned \Nto stone with crumble into dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be any way to restore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:07.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus acts bad, but he \Nain't gonna go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:11.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he gets on my nerves, but \Nhe's a fellow guild member.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bluff, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a fighting festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But then why can't I get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:21.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can go through normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:25.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People over 80 years old \Ncan't pass through...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:27.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean I'm over 80?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you are, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:34.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You call Laxus your fellow member?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:37.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe that he'll go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's 2 hours and 18 minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:45.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are... 42 people left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:51.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,42 people? More than half are \Ngone after the infighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:55.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Purple Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:02.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Smoke Fake. You're getting rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:06.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been too soft on people...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The East Forest... The East Forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:16.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to see Poluchka and get a \Npotion to cure Erza and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:26.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the runes set up around the entire city?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will allow no one to break my rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Freed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:39.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus should have told you that the \Nfield of battle was the entire city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:43.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a wizard, then \Nfight! Show me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:50.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, where are those Raijin Tribe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:55.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are Bicslow's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:03.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evergreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a Man, then don't take hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:14.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Return my sister and the others to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:18.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:25.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I love flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:28.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They look so good... on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:35.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that's cute \Nabout you is your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:42.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Return my sister and the others to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:46.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you beat me while you're blindfolded?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:58.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So you can tell where I am by smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:03.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad though, because you \Nare already inside my Fairy Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Bomb, Gremlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I love statues.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:23.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how ugly a monster might be, they \Nbecome a beautiful work of art when turned to stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, gaze at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:30.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give your body up to beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:38.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evergreen vs. Elfman. Winner: Evergreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:40.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman: Out of commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:42.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Elfman got beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:47.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray's fighting Bicslow! I wanna join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:50.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reedus is fighting Freed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Raijin Tribe has started \Nto make their move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:57.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's settle this fight, man to man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, man to girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you turned to stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic wore off, and I came after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you don't know the tricks this \Nman, I mean woman, has up her sleeves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:20.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even have the courage to \Nface me like a man, I mean woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:23.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:30.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake you made with your magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:35.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a wizard who can make anything \Nhe paints come to life, after all. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:40.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't known that, \NI might have been fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Freed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:48.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, don't \Nhurt anyone any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't that kind of man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:10:00.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle of Fairy Tail... 40 people left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reedus was beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured Freed could do it! Look at him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:10.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the time to be impressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:13.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can't get any help from Poluchka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:14.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need any.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:17.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole turning to dust thing is a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm bluffing, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:22.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a thought projection!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:28.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you still here, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:36.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your members... Well, I guess \Nyou call them your children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:40.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you can't stand watching your \Nchildren destroy each other, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and Erza can't join in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:47.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one left who could \Ndefeat my Raijin Tribe, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna give in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray's still there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's about as strong as Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He ain't gonna lose to no Raijin Tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:00.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't put much faith in that brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:11.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate Gray, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Line Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, Victory Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Babies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:36.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,X Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:49.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:57.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Part of my Seith Magic is the ability \Nto possess the souls of dolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:12:02.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you freeze the dolls, I can \Ntransfer their souls to other bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:05.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:08.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's gonna be annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:22.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it? No matter how many \Nof my dolls you destroy, it's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:25.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll freeze you directly instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:29.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and try!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:30.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, trying to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:34.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Up here, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:52.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you! I want to play \Nwith strong opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:56.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My babies are gettin' all bored recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:58.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Runes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:04.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Using magic is prohibited for those within \Nthe barrier until the battle is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of Freed's traps?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:11.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess a long-distance wizard like \Nmyself has a bit of an advantage here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:24.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that without your magic, \Nyou'd be completely helpless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:25.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't cut it, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, honey. Stand back from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:53.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:59.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why that little... And after he \Ngot hit by my babies like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:15.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My extra clothing helped cushion against the \Ndamage... Don't go scaring me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:19.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should wear some heavy \Nclothing sometimes, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:25.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray is out of commission. 28 people left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See, didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:36.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! I'm sure that he used some dirty trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:41.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So who will beat the Raijin Tribe now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:47.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad. Doesn't seem \Nlike he's participatin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:51.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't actually give a \Ndamn about the guild anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:56.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't get out, it \Nwon't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, stop this Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:15.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The high and mighty Master of Fairy Tail \Ncan't go surrendering at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:22.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you insist, then how about you \Ngive up your position as Master to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's playing dirty, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:27.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared a me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that your goal all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:35.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only one and a half hours \Nuntil the statues crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:41.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to retire, use the guild's loudspeakers\Nand announce it so the whole town can hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:45.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "I'm giving up my position \Nas Master of Fairy Tail to Laxus!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:52.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is more important, your \Nposition or your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:16:00.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't fight me, how \Nare you the strongest?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:01.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be the master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:05.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about being master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:11.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I cannot entrust Fairy Tail to Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:14.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't understand the \Nweight of the positoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He lacks conviction and heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But at this rate Lucy and the \Nothers will turn to dust...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:23.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has to defeat \NLaxus and his gang, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:30.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel, that's where you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat the dishware!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bone to pick with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:40.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:49.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you also 80?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:53.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At about that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gremlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:02.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:07.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Bicslow! We're your allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:10.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not on the side of weaklings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't that right, babies?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:18.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Freed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alzack...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:26.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your runes, I've \Nhurt my friends too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:30.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told myself it was to change \NBisca back to normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:40.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guns Magic! Tornado Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He sliced through the wind magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:58.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're using some strange \Nmagic other than the runes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bisca...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:07.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who uses magic inside these \Nrunes will be deprived of oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:12.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was use runes \Nto their fullest effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:19.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think there's anyone who can beat \Nme under my rules? Me, the creator?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:25.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle of Fairy Tail.  So, 2 are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only 2 are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:30.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you get out either?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:31.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop copyin' me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:32.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:35.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm hungry, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:40.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:46.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wasn't even counted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:49.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no more wizards left to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:50.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:53.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. Guess I better revive Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:54.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:58.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought I could finally show up Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't she melt if I heat her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the stone shell...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:11.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza and the others have \Nturned to stone completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:13.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't know 'till we try, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You want to kill Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:17.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Broil her nice and good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to rub her with flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey buddy, not so frisky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, she broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Glue, glue! Happy, get the glue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:31.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! You think that'll fix her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:35.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your flames on my iron, and \Nwe'll weld her back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:36.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:40.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:42.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it you, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:53.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:56.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:58.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:01.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:05.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's because of my right eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:12.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! The artificial eye must have \Nlowered the effect of the magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:15.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, do you know what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:20.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Even though I was turned \Nto stone, I could hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:23.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! It's time for a counter attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,3 remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:30.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With me restored, the number \Nremaining changed appropriately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:32.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:36.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three are Natsu, \NGajeel, and Erza, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,4 remaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It increased?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:41.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is still stone... Then who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:51.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more out there, \Nremember? Outside of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:54.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean... Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:55.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:57.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean he's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:21:02.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the real war is about to \Nbegin. This is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:04.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:10.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Another possible candidate for \Nthe strongest in Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:12.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:18.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's restored and \NMystogan joins the fray...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:22.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Including me, that's the \Ntop three in Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:25.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be a festival without the best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:29.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You showed up earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:36.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with the outfit, Erza-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, a bunch of young \Nfolks from your place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:42.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,have been fighting around the \Ncity and causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:45.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. It's part of the \Npreparations for the grand parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.69,0:21:48.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some strange preparations all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:49.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:51.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:53.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to fight so much though, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:04.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you return from \Na statue back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:09.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fine by me. It just means I \Nget to have fun tormenting you more!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:10.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evergreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:15.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really make me angry. Why are \Nyou the Fairy Queen, Titania?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:19.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the number one fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:33.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That time we laughed, saying "we're both like each other,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:43.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,we even kindly overlooked the little lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:49.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose a place to go back to together, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:58.72,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'll protect that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:03.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The meetings and partings numerous as the stars in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:05.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,All the things I don't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:10.29,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I feel like I don't need any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:15.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to see you by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:21.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,all my happiness and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.07,0:23:23.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start our tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:30.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it like we've just been reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:36.20,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Like flowers blown in a summer wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:44.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,let us bloom brightly in this instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.06,0:23:59.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, if you keep baring your stomach, \Nyour belly button will get stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:02.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You can steal belly buttons?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:03.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Lucy said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:06.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stick out your stomach \Nwhen lightning strikes,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.49,0:24:09.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the god of lightning will \Ntake your belly button away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.08,0:24:11.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Happy, you don't have a belly button.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.47,0:24:16.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:18.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.89,0:24:22.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only rumbling I'm scared \Nof is Gramps' grumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.38,0:24:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good one. Give him a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.83,0:24:27.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
